(i) National Economic and Development Authority (NEDA);

(j) National Commission for Culture and the Arts (NCCA);

(k) Philippine Information Agency (PIA);

(l) Philippine International Trading Corporation (PITC); and

(m) Technical Education and Skills Development Authority (TESDA).
